let activeGrade = "All";

function renderFixtures() {
  const tbody = document.getElementById("fixture-tbody");
  const cardsEl = document.getElementById("fixture-cards");
  tbody.innerHTML = "";
  cardsEl.innerHTML = "";

  fixtures.forEach(f => {
    const show = activeGrade === "All" || f.grade === activeGrade;
    const isBye = f.venue === "BYE";
    const dot = isBye ? "" : f.home
      ? `<span class="home-marker"></span>`
      : `<span class="away-marker"></span>`;

    // Table row
    const tr = document.createElement("tr");
    if (!show) tr.classList.add("hidden-row");
    tr.innerHTML = `
      <td class="date-col">${f.date}</td>
      <td class="round-col">${f.round}</td>
      <td><span class="grade-pill ${f.grade}">${f.grade === "Womens" ? "Women's" : f.grade}</span></td>
      <td>${dot}${f.match}</td>
      <td class="venue-col">${f.venue}</td>`;
    tbody.appendChild(tr);

    // Mobile card
    const card = document.createElement("div");
    card.className = `fix-card ${f.grade}`;
    if (!show) card.classList.add("hidden-row");
    card.innerHTML = `
      <div class="fix-card-top">
        <span class="fix-card-date">${f.date}</span>
        <span class="fix-card-rnd">Rd ${f.round}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="fix-card-match">${isBye ? "" : dot}${f.match}</div>
      <div class="fix-card-meta">
        <span class="grade-pill ${f.grade}">${f.grade === "Womens" ? "Women's" : f.grade}</span>
        <span class="fix-card-venue">${f.venue}</span>
      </div>`;
    cardsEl.appendChild(card);
  });
}

document.querySelectorAll(".filter-btn").forEach(btn => {
  btn.addEventListener("click", () => {
    document.querySelectorAll(".filter-btn").forEach(b => b.classList.remove("active"));
    btn.classList.add("active");
    activeGrade = btn.dataset.grade;
    renderFixtures();
  });
});

renderFixtures();
</script>
